This is a placeholder for HR_Onboarding.xlsx

In a real implementation, this would be an Excel file with the following structure:

Column Headers (Row 1):
- Employee Name
- Date of Birth
- Residential Address
- Contact Phone
- Email Address
- Previous Company
- Job Title
- Start Date
- Salary
- Emergency Contact
- Emergency Phone
- Bank Account Number
- PAN Number

The form filler would extract data from uploaded documents and populate these fields.
